{
  "stem": "7832.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mainly they were trying to put a lot of clothing on our bodies so we don't have heavy things to carry, because they put other things in our-- in our suitcases to carry.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they put-- like I had like five or six skirts on me and tops, and my head was covered, like they put these babushkas on my head.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- we were just dressed, overly dressed, so we could have extra stuff too, because we were only allowed to take so much.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the suitcases were for other things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But one thing my mother did is she-- she took diamonds, and they-- and she rolled diamonds into one of my skirts and my sister.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, my sister was only 4 1/2 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I guess that was a way of putting-- preserving things, or-- you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said to me to take care of that one skirt in case I have to go to work in a different place where she's going to work, then to take care of that skirt, and during the time if I don't have anything to eat, to take out the diamonds and buy bread.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what that is for, but be very careful not to lose it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I knew that there was that in the-- in the bottom of my skirt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and we went on a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were fortunate that we were-- we were trying to stay back, not to get on a train before our cousins came in from the city and we were going to go together with them.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we heard-- we didn't see it, but we heard that a man came in from the city and he knew my father.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, don't wait for your cousin.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
